data.description: Beautiful Lennar home with a spacious and flexible floor plan. Attached suite with separate entrance and kitchenette, ideal for mult-generational living. Main floor features an oversized family room, open chef's kitchen with large island, and eating area with access to a covered patio, perfet for entertaining. Upstairs you'll find the primary suite with spa-like bath and walk-in closet, verstaile loft space and laundry, a large bonus space, and 2 addtionals bedrooms. Smart home automation. Enjoy having AC for those hot summer days. Amazing convenient location with great freeway access.
